  "description": "A stunning nighttime photograph captures a vibrant fireworks display over a cityscape and a bridge. The fireworks explode in a burst of red, white, and blue, creating a dramatic contrast against the dark sky. Below, a long, illuminated bridge stretches across the water, connecting the city to what appears to be a distant landmass. The city skyline is a tapestry of twinkling lights, with taller buildings standing out against the lower structures. The water below is dark and reflective, mirroring the lights above. The overall composition emphasizes the grandeur and festive atmosphere of the scene.",
